00:26:51,240 --> 00:26:52,490
Take care.

309
00:26:59,770 --> 00:27:00,310
We are leaving.

310
00:27:00,930 --> 00:27:01,630
Take care.

311
00:27:04,680 --> 00:27:07,090
It's been a long time since I
