312
00:27:07,600 --> 00:27:08,800
You should be stepping up

313
00:27:08,800 --> 00:27:10,280
to realize your dream.

314
00:27:11,170 --> 00:27:14,260
It will take a while to quit your voice,

315
00:27:14,970 --> 00:27:16,010
but you already have

316
00:27:16,010 --> 00:27:17,740
something you really want to do.

317
00:27:18,310 --> 00:27:19,440
I will also try hard to move forward.

318
00:27:20,330 --> 00:27:22,110
Will you check

319
00:27:22,110 --> 00:27:22,840
this broadcasting station again?

320
00:27:23,710 --> 00:27:25,060
