My offer and scholarship!

325
00:28:09,910 --> 00:28:11,830
Report to school.

326
00:28:18,960 --> 00:28:20,610
Only two months left.

327
00:28:33,390 --> 00:28:34,190
Thank you.

328
00:28:36,890 --> 00:28:37,590
What are you doing?

329
00:28:39,070 --> 00:28:39,790
What?

