343
00:30:03,370 --> 00:30:05,000
The floral dress.

344
00:30:10,960 --> 00:30:12,260
This piece

345
00:30:14,960 --> 00:30:17,530
is cute and has a lace pattern
that suits you.

346
00:30:17,530 --> 00:30:19,020
No, I can't buy clothes.

347
00:30:19,020 --> 00:30:20,760
Just take a try.

348
00:30:20,760 --> 00:30:21,540
It's okay.

349
00:30:23,470 --> 00:30:24,720
Let's look around.

350
00:30:24,960 --> 00:30:26,830
Well, I think that one is fine.

351
00:30:26,830 --> 00:30:28,170
- Which one?
- The one we just looked.

352
00:30:28,170 --> 00:30:29,790
The one with floral patterns?

353
00:30:29,790 --> 00:30:31,330
Okay, take a try later.

354
00:30:36,030 --> 00:30:37,100
What's this?

355
00:30:37,100 --> 00:30:39,740
Aunt, I think this one looks good.

356
00:30:40,560 --> 00:30:41,880
This one

357
00:30:43,060 --> 00:30:44,510
may make me younger.

358
00:30:44,900 --> 00:30:47,930
But would it be appropriate for me
to wear it at my age?

359
00:30:48,020 --> 00:30:48,860
How come?

360
00:30:48,860 --> 00:30:50,540
It can show your temperament

361
00:30:50,760 --> 00:30:52,910
and flatter your skin tone.

362
00:30:52,910 --> 00:30:54,990
You have fair complexion. Just take a try.

363
00:30:55,820 --> 00:30:56,770
Okay, as you say.

364
00:30:56,770 --> 00:30:57,620
Let me try it.

365
00:30:58,060 --> 00:30:58,700
Excuse me.

366
00:31:02,720 --> 00:31:04,040
So nice.

367
00:31:04,040 --> 00:31:04,840
Really?

368
00:31:04,840 --> 00:31:06,000
I mean it.

369
00:31:06,680 --> 00:31:08,730
Uncle Ye would love it.

370
00:31:12,410 --> 00:31:14,250
When we were young and in love,

371
00:31:14,880 --> 00:31:17,340
he always bought me clothes

372
00:31:17,600 --> 00:31:18,930
and jewelries.

373
00:31:19,660 --> 00:31:21,640
I kept them all.

374
00:31:22,240 --> 00:31:24,880
And there are five boxes of them.

375
00:31:25,060 --> 00:31:25,630
Five boxes?

376
00:31:25,630 --> 00:31:26,160
Yes.

377
00:31:30,680 --> 00:31:33,020
Uncle Ye loves you so much.

378
00:31:33,580 --> 00:31:35,430
Yes, he treats me well.

379
00:31:36,070 --> 00:31:38,180
Not only material needs,

380
00:31:38,330 --> 00:31:40,490
in other respects, he also grants
whatever is requested.

381
00:31:41,580 --> 00:31:43,550
You don't have to envy me.

382
00:31:44,000 --> 00:31:44,820
Listen.

383
00:31:44,820 --> 00:31:46,430
My son

384
00:31:46,780 --> 00:31:48,040
is quite like his dad in this respect.

385
00:31:49,200 --> 00:31:50,510
Come on, let's take a seat.

386
00:32:02,570 --> 00:32:03,530
Erduo, look.

387
00:32:05,070 --> 00:32:07,580
When I was packing my jewelries
the other day,

388
00:32:08,270 --> 00:32:11,000
I found this pair of earrings
suitable for you.

389
00:32:11,930 --> 00:32:13,930
So I took it for you.

390
00:32:14,560 --> 00:32:16,990
Aunt, it's way too precious.

391
00:32:17,210 --> 00:32:18,130
I can't take it.

392
00:32:18,560 --> 00:32:19,350
You have to.

393
00:32:19,810 --> 00:32:20,610
You know what?

394
00:32:21,080 --> 00:32:22,990
This was the first gift his dad gave me

395
00:32:23,270 --> 00:32:24,800
when we fell in love.

396
00:32:25,620 --> 00:32:27,010
I am giving it to you now

397
00:32:27,010 --> 00:32:29,100
to pass it on from generation to generation.

398
00:32:29,100 --> 00:32:30,370
No way, aunt.

399
00:32:30,370 --> 00:32:31,790
No more refusal.

400
00:32:31,790 --> 00:32:32,430
Just take it.

401
00:32:32,930 --> 00:32:33,410
Listen to my words.

402
00:32:38,500 --> 00:32:40,050
I heard from Shuwei

403
00:32:40,260 --> 00:32:42,840
that you were also a famous violinist
at that time.

404
00:32:47,320 --> 00:32:50,590
Well, I have loved music since I was a child.

405
00:32:50,810 --> 00:32:53,820
I chose to play the violin later on.

406
00:32:55,090 --> 00:32:58,230
I intended to reach a higher level in art

407
00:32:59,130 --> 00:33:01,090
at a young age.

408
00:33:02,650 --> 00:33:04,280
But I met his dad later.

409
00:33:05,800 --> 00:33:08,870
So I gradually gave up on world tours.

410
00:33:12,640 --> 00:33:16,070
Do you think it a pity?

411
00:33:19,820 --> 00:33:22,570
Although his dad is like a kidult now,

412
00:33:22,820 --> 00:33:25,100
he was quite serious when he was young.

413
00:33:25,670 --> 00:33:28,390
I remember when I was on world tours,

414
00:33:29,270 --> 00:33:34,130
he often finished work overnight

415
00:33:34,380 --> 00:33:35,860
and stayed by my side.

416
00:33:37,550 --> 00:33:39,540
Seeing him working so hard,

417
00:33:42,480 --> 00:33:44,610
I gradually reduced my work.

418
00:33:46,960 --> 00:33:49,030
Maybe it's just a choice.

419
00:33:49,990 --> 00:33:51,960
Every time I saw him

420
00:33:51,960 --> 00:33:54,280
willingly pay for me,

421
00:33:55,780 --> 00:33:57,080
I felt that

422
00:33:58,220 --> 00:34:00,850
everything else

423
00:34:01,420 --> 00:34:03,010
was less important.

424
00:34:03,590 --> 00:34:04,720
Right, Erduo?

425
00:34:06,710 --> 00:34:10,090
Kid, my only wish right now

426
00:34:10,640 --> 00:34:13,520
is for you and Shuwei to be safe, healthy

427
00:34:14,300 --> 00:34:15,710
and together forever.

428
00:34:21,240 --> 00:34:22,990
All right. Let's look around.

429
00:34:23,120 --> 00:34:23,720
Sure.

430
00:34:23,720 --> 00:34:24,280
Let's go.

431
00:34:30,250 --> 00:34:31,320
You have been searching information
for a long time.

432
00:34:32,020 --> 00:34:32,680
Aren't you tired?

433
00:34:34,360 --> 00:34:36,330
Well, look.

434
00:34:37,750 --> 00:34:40,510
These are a few routes I planned.

435
00:34:40,720 --> 00:34:41,960
It won't take a long time,

436
00:34:41,960 --> 00:34:43,920
but there will be many tourist attractions.

437
00:34:44,340 --> 00:34:45,160
What do you think?

438
00:34:47,350 --> 00:34:47,830
No problem.

439
00:34:51,980 --> 00:34:52,780
What about the place to live?

440
00:34:53,290 --> 00:34:55,070
Any requests?

441
00:34:55,580 --> 00:34:58,190
Would you like to stay in an ordinary hotel

442
00:34:58,190 --> 00:35:00,230
or a unique homestay?

443
00:35:00,750 --> 00:35:02,510
But I checked.

444
00:35:02,960 --> 00:35:06,770
Hotels and homestays near the scenic spot

445
00:35:07,180 --> 00:35:08,320
cost a lot.

446
00:35:08,790 --> 00:35:10,320
While the accommodation
further away from the scenic spot

447
00:35:12,000 --> 00:35:15,120
is cheap but inconvenient to travel.

448
00:35:18,190 --> 00:35:20,880
Don't think about me, choose one as you like.

449
00:35:22,750 --> 00:35:24,960
But it's a trip of us two.

450
00:35:25,320 --> 00:35:26,600
It can't be all up to me.

451
00:35:26,600 --> 00:35:27,660
Just choose one.

452
00:35:29,510 --> 00:35:30,020
All right.

453
00:35:30,350 --> 00:35:32,220
I would choose the farther one
with a better environment.

454
00:35:39,600 --> 00:35:41,920
Accommodation is done.

455
00:35:52,320 --> 00:35:52,810
Everyone,

456
00:35:53,980 --> 00:35:55,960
I have something to announce to you all.

457
00:35:58,470 --> 00:36:00,040
For my personal reasons,

458
00:36:00,360 --> 00:36:01,470
I'm going to Japan

459
00:36:02,160 --> 00:36:03,180
next week

460
00:36:04,170 --> 00:36:05,130
for two years.

461
00:36:07,550 --> 00:36:09,330
Our studio will work as usual.

462
00:36:10,530 --> 00:36:11,880
But since I have no way

463
00:36:12,280 --> 00:36:13,910
to participate in any production
during this period of time,

464
00:36:14,720 --> 00:36:15,770
from today on,

465
00:36:16,350 --> 00:36:18,840
I won't take any orders

466
00:36:18,840 --> 00:36:20,010
of advanced customization violins

467
00:36:20,860 --> 00:36:21,710
that need to be made by me.

468
00:36:23,220 --> 00:36:24,480
The recovery time will be decided

469
00:36:25,340 --> 00:36:26,480
after I return from Japan.

470
00:36:28,740 --> 00:36:29,460
At last,

471
00:36:30,950 --> 00:36:32,610
I will also officially decline

472
00:36:32,610 --> 00:36:34,200
the previous violin production order

473
00:36:35,950 --> 00:36:36,950
from the Vienna Philharmonic.

474
00:36:38,060 --> 00:36:40,150
Boss, don't you want

475
00:36:40,150 --> 00:36:41,380
to take this order?

476
00:36:41,610 --> 00:36:43,970
It's such a rare opportunity

477
00:36:44,330 --> 00:36:45,770
and not through seeking.

478
00:36:46,880 --> 00:36:49,040
We can understand that you
cut back business after you go to Japan.

479
00:36:49,520 --> 00:36:51,080
But it's not in your style

480
00:36:51,390 --> 00:36:52,380
that you give up

481
00:36:53,050 --> 00:36:54,480
such an important order.

482
00:36:54,480 --> 00:36:55,230
I've made up my mind.

483
00:36:58,040 --> 00:36:58,990
Hope you can understand me.

484
00:37:10,220 --> 00:37:10,750
Come over.

485
00:37:14,110 --> 00:37:14,940
Charging time.

486
00:37:17,700 --> 00:37:18,520
Are you tired?

487
00:37:21,490 --> 00:37:22,580
Exhausted.

488
00:37:24,150 --> 00:37:25,150
Would you like to eat hot pot?

489
00:37:28,500 --> 00:37:30,090
I prefer eat at home.

490
00:37:34,210 --> 00:37:36,020
Okay, let's go home then.

491
00:37:37,370 --> 00:37:37,990
Let's go.

492
00:37:40,340 --> 00:37:40,790
Here.

493
00:37:47,060 --> 00:37:49,660
Chef Ye, are you ready?

494
00:37:50,060 --> 00:37:51,780
There are plenty of dishes.

495
00:37:51,780 --> 00:37:53,920
It would be a waste.

496
00:37:54,560 --> 00:37:56,450
Almost done.

497
00:38:03,380 --> 00:38:04,830
Just one more soup.

498
00:38:07,450 --> 00:38:09,980
Shuwei, let's have a good talk.

499
00:38:10,380 --> 00:38:13,070
It's only good for you, nothing bad.

500
00:38:13,580 --> 00:38:15,050
Leaving our business aside,

501
00:38:15,050 --> 00:38:16,880
don't you care about

502
00:38:16,880 --> 00:38:18,260
your apprenticeship with my dad?

503
00:38:18,620 --> 00:38:19,970
I'll wait for your call.

504
00:38:19,970 --> 00:38:22,200
Please don't let my dad down, okay?

505
00:38:22,610 --> 00:38:23,030
Done.

506
00:38:28,660 --> 00:38:30,870
Can we eat so much meat?

507
00:38:31,550 --> 00:38:32,680
More food, more nutrition.

508
00:38:33,080 --> 00:38:34,330
You have been working hard lately.

509
00:38:35,520 --> 00:38:37,420
I remember that when I was injured,

510
00:38:38,090 --> 00:38:39,690
you often prepared swine brains for me.

511
00:38:43,690 --> 00:38:45,160
More food, more nutrition.

512
00:38:45,660 --> 00:38:47,670
It sounds like

513
00:38:49,210 --> 00:38:50,050
you're raising a pig.

514
00:38:52,190 --> 00:38:53,810
So is this a food chain?

515
00:38:53,810 --> 00:38:55,450
You feed me first.

516
00:38:55,450 --> 00:38:56,790
Then eat me.

517
00:38:57,180 --> 00:38:59,050
No wonder there is warning
not to eat too much,

518
00:38:59,050 --> 00:39:00,870
otherwise you will be eaten.

519
00:39:03,990 --> 00:39:04,780
It's too late

520
00:39:05,510 --> 00:39:06,270
to realize it now.

521
00:39:07,970 --> 00:39:08,360
Let's eat.

522
00:39:34,820 --> 00:39:35,540
Hello.

523
00:39:36,390 --> 00:39:37,200
Hello, Erduo.

524
00:39:37,970 --> 00:39:39,250
This is Lin Qingzhuo.

525
00:39:43,440 --> 00:39:44,250
Hello.

526
00:39:44,910 --> 00:39:45,860
Long time no see.

527
00:39:45,860 --> 00:39:46,830
How are you doing recently?

528
00:39:46,830 --> 00:39:48,390
Is the tour going well?

529
00:39:49,000 --> 00:39:49,960
Yes.

530
00:39:50,700 --> 00:39:52,110
I am in America now.

531
00:39:52,110 --> 00:39:53,930
There is another show tomorrow night.

532
00:39:55,880 --> 00:39:58,550
It should be daytime where you are.

533
00:39:59,110 --> 00:39:59,640
Yes.

534
00:40:01,180 --> 00:40:03,720
Erduo, I thought for a long time

535
00:40:03,720 --> 00:40:05,880
and decided to call you.

536
00:40:07,030 --> 00:40:08,600
It's about Shuwei.

537
00:40:11,050 --> 00:40:12,180
Ye Shuwei?

538
00:40:14,850 --> 00:40:17,210
It may be inappropriate for me to say this,

539
00:40:17,670 --> 00:40:20,070
but I hope you could let him go properly

540
00:40:20,070 --> 00:40:21,140
and set him free.

541
00:40:22,880 --> 00:40:23,960
What do you mean?

542
00:40:25,640 --> 00:40:27,550
Has he never told you?

543
00:40:32,000 --> 00:40:33,050
Told me what?

544
00:40:33,500 --> 00:40:34,860
My dad got sick

545
00:40:35,330 --> 00:40:37,120
and lost the ability to make violins.

546
00:40:37,660 --> 00:40:38,910
The level of apprentices

547
00:40:38,910 --> 00:40:40,730
in the workshop is uneven,

548
00:40:41,130 --> 00:40:42,840
so many orders have been backlogged.

549
00:40:43,140 --> 00:40:44,660
My dad has always been

550
00:40:44,660 --> 00:40:45,930
thinking highly of Shuwei.

551
00:40:46,650 --> 00:40:48,820
He hopes him to come back and
to take over the workshop.

552
00:40:49,480 --> 00:40:51,660
For some personal reasons,

553
00:40:52,110 --> 00:40:53,200
I came back last time

554
00:40:53,520 --> 00:40:55,390
to discuss this matter with him, too.

555
00:40:56,160 --> 00:40:58,330
I know that although he said
he would consider it,

556
00:40:58,860 --> 00:40:59,940
he didn't

557
00:40:59,940 --> 00:41:01,960
take it seriously at all.

558
00:41:05,430 --> 00:41:07,160
Why did you call me?

559
00:41:07,730 --> 00:41:10,350
I know he declined the offer because of you.

560
00:41:11,760 --> 00:41:14,150
I thought he once told you about it.

561
00:41:16,110 --> 00:41:17,380
Erduo, you know what?

562
00:41:17,840 --> 00:41:20,080
After Shuwei left my dad
to work independently,

563
00:41:20,520 --> 00:41:22,440
he went through a period of silence
for several years.

564
00:41:23,500 --> 00:41:25,620
He paid a lot of effort into the studio

565
00:41:25,840 --> 00:41:28,460
to make it what it is now.

566
00:41:29,810 --> 00:41:31,730
My dad's violin brand

567
00:41:31,730 --> 00:41:33,840
is quite influential in Italy.

568
00:41:34,730 --> 00:41:38,200
If he runs these two studios together,

569
00:41:38,200 --> 00:41:41,130
I am sure he will achieve even more
in the future.

570
00:41:44,320 --> 00:41:46,720
I say this just in the hope

571
00:41:47,730 --> 00:41:50,140
that they can continue

572
00:41:50,140 --> 00:41:51,850
their painstaking effort.

573
00:41:55,040 --> 00:41:58,420
So you want me to persuade him?

574
00:41:59,680 --> 00:42:00,270
Yes.

575
00:42:01,150 --> 00:42:03,610
He has been avoiding my contact lately.

576
00:42:04,650 --> 00:42:05,930
So I had no choice

